{"tid":36180,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"School Food 呢間嘢真係on99","createTime":"2016-12-12T13:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T07:15:22.000Z","uid":798,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32c1558463737601bb91d98120083564f008443d","tid":36180,"uid":798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:57:53.000Z","msg":"我發覺泡菜仔真係窮撚到仆街<br />\n啲咁嘅死人食物主要材料永遠係<br />\n1 醃菜<br />\n2 肉乾<br />\n3 蛋<br />\n4 紫菜<br />\n5 飯<br />\n6 年糕<br />\n7 飯<br />\n8 飯<br />\n<br />\n低能<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4o3n85j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4o3n85j.jpg&h=f1fbd2f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成碟嘢成本都唔知洗唔洗十蚊，夠膽死收人幾十蚊<br />\n<br />\n真係得啲on9港女同啲on9港女男朋友先會食<br />\n唔係我條女講一句 人一世物一世乜都試下<br />\n我真係寧願食山哥勿演<br />\n<br />\n好在我唔輸蝕，串咗佢一句：人一世物一世又唔見你食屎？"},{"pid":"70d21757134337525ea3fd996a0870fae2998849","tid":36180,"uid":52323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T18:02:12.000Z","msg":"成本撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5234439dd4b8b9869ab80c2d6079d14c2e7e345d","tid":36180,"uid":4236,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T18:04:04.000Z","msg":"真係好撚柒貴又少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6519efd7c052fa7280f4993c763086f7836e85d","tid":36180,"uid":48894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T18:11:31.000Z","msg":"school food冇錯<br />\n錯既係泡菜狗文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18d6d7f967920561a4d558775d8eb490a9489e03","tid":36180,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T18:14:29.000Z","msg":"你漏左芝屎呀"},{"pid":"